These are Puzzles for 2x6 Level 7

.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-1::.
The people prefer 6 different music-genres: trance, ambient, disco, punk, techno, funk
6 different pets are kept: hamster, frog, turtle, ferret, goat, snake
 1. the fan of disco is in an odd position##4
 2. the fan of funk is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
 3. the fan of techno is not the owner of the goat##6
 4. the fan of punk is somewhere to the left of the fan of ambient##5
 5. the owner of the goat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the turtle##5
 6. the owner of the frog is somewhere to the right of the owner of the turtle##5
 7. the owner of the goat is not the fan of ambient##6
 8. the owner of the snake is in an odd position##4
 9. the fan of trance is somewhere between the owner of the snake and the fan of punk##7
10. the owner of the turtle is on the left or right of the owner of the ferret##3
11. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the right of the owner of the hamster##5
12. the owner of the snake is somewhere to the left of the owner of the ferret##5
13. the owner of the hamster is the fan of trance##1
14. the owner of the turtle is somewhere to the left of the fan of techno##5
15. the fan of funk is the owner of the ferret##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1   |   2   |   3    |    4     |     5      |    6     |
| Music-Genre   | punk   | trance | disco   | funk     | ambient    | techno   |
| Pet           | goat | hamster   | snake | ferret | turtle | frog |

