.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-2::.
The people perfer 6 different movie-genres: romance, zombie, scientific, animation, family, western
6 different pets are kept: goldfish, turtle, rat, lizard, goat, hedgehog
 1. the person watching romance movies is somewhere to the right of the person watching zombie movies##5
 2. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 3. the owner of the goat is on the left or right of the person watching family movies##3
 4. the person watching scientific movies is on the left or right of the owner of the lizard##3
 5. the person watching western movies is on the left of the owner of the goat##1
 6. the person watching family movies is on the left or right of the person watching scientific movies##3
 7. the person watching family movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching scientific movies##5
 8. the person watching romance movies is on the far left or far right##3
 9. the person watching family movies is not the owner of the goat##6
10. the owner of the goldfish is somewhere between the owner of the hedgehog and the owner of the lizard##7
11. the owner of the rat is somewhere to the left of the person watching family movies##5
12. the person watching western movies is on the right of the owner of the turtle##1
13. the owner of the hedgehog is on the left or right of the owner of the goldfish##3
14. the owner of the hedgehog is in an even position##4
15. the person watching animation movies is somewhere to the left of the owner of the lizard##5
16. the owner of the hedgehog is on the right of the owner of the goldfish##1
17. the person watching animation movies is somewhere between the owner of the turtle and the person watching family movies##7

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |      2      |    3    |     4      |     5      |    6     |
| Movie-Genre   | zombie | western | animation | family     | scientific      | romance |
| Pet           | turtle         | rat        | goat   | lizard | goldfish | hedgehog    |

