.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-3::.
There are 6 different favourite beverages: almond-milk, mirinda, juice, sprite, 7up, coffee
The people prefer 6 different types of sport: rowing, snowboarding, badminton, soccer, ice-hockey, coffee-polo
 1. the person drinking juice is on the left of the person drinking mirinda##1
 2. the person drinking almond-milk is in an even position##4
 3. the person who's sport is soccer is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
 4. the person who's sport is snowboarding is not the person drinking sprite##6
 5. the person drinking almond-milk is not the person who's sport is rowing##6
 6. the person who's sport is soccer is on the right of the person who's sport is coffee-polo##1
 7. the person who's sport is snowboarding is on the far left##1
 8. the person drinking 7up is somewhere to the left of the person drinking coffee##5
 9. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking mirinda##3
10. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere between the person drinking 7up and the person drinking mirinda##7
11. the person who's sport is coffee-polo is in an odd position##4
12. the person who's sport is rowing is on the left or right of the person drinking almond-milk##3
13. the person drinking almond-milk is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is rowing##5
14. the person drinking sprite is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is coffee-polo##5

.:: Answer ::.
|            |     1      |    2     |    3     |    4    |    5     |       6       |
| Beverage   | 7up        | sprite | coffee    | almond-milk    | juice | mirinda |
| Sport      | snowboarding | ice-hockey  | coffee-polo | soccer | rowing | badminton      |

