 3. the person watching sports movies is somewhere to the right of the person drinking fanta##5
 4. the person drinking juice is on the right of the person drinking fanta##1
 5. the person watching sports movies is not the person drinking fanta##6
 6. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking iced-tea and the person drinking fanta##7
 7. the person drinking milk is somewhere between the person drinking juice and the person drinking iced-tea##7
 8. the person drinking sprite is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 9. the person watching musical movies is somewhere between the person drinking milk and the person drinking cola##7
10. the person watching thriller movies is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
11. the person drinking fanta is on the right of the person drinking milk##1
12. the person watching martial-arts movies is somewhere to the left of the person watching sports movies##5
13. the person watching epic movies is the person drinking cola##1
14. the person watching musical movies is somewhere to the left of the person drinking juice##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |      2      |   3   |       4       |    5    |   6   |
| Beverage      | cola | sprite | iced-tea | milk | fanta | juice   |
| Movie-Genre   | epic  | thriller      | musical | satire     | martial-arts | sports |

