11. the owner of the goat is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1
12. the person driving the jet-ski is somewhere between the owner of the horse and the person driving the ship##7
13. the owner of the cat is somewhere to the left of the owner of the mouse##5

.:: Answer ::.
|             |   1   |   2    |     3     |   4    |  5   |     6      |
| Pet         | turtle   | cat | frog      | goat | mouse  | horse   |
| Transport   | car | scooter  | ship | snowmobile   | jet-ski | taxi |

