.:: Puzzle 2x6-Level-7-20::.
The people have 6 different hobbies: singing, dancing, card-games, fishing, hiking, puzzles
The people have 6 different jobs:  teacher, writer, police-officer, engineer, pilot, firefighter
 1. the person who's hobby is hiking is on the left or right of the person who's hobby is puzzles##3
 2. the person who's hobby is card-games is on the left of the person who's hobby is fishing##1
 3. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the police-officer##5
 4. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere between the engineer and the writer##7
 5. the firefighter is on the left or right of the police-officer##3
 6. the person who's hobby is card-games is the pilot##1
 7. the person who's hobby is hiking is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
 8. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is singing##5
 9. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the police-officer##5
10. the writer is somewhere to the right of the firefighter##5
11. the firefighter is on the right of the police-officer##1
12. the person who's hobby is singing is somewhere to the right of the engineer##5
13. the person who's hobby is dancing is somewhere between the person who's hobby is singing and the person who's hobby is card-games##7
14. the writer is on the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##1
15. the pilot is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is hiking##5

.:: Answer ::.
|         |        1        |      2      |     3      |     4     |      5      |     6      |
| Hobby   | card-games         | fishing | dancing | singing   | puzzles | hiking  |
| Job     | pilot | engineer  | police-officer  | firefighter | writer  | teacher |

 